216
00:07:11,280 --> 00:07:14,920
To answer this question,

217
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:16,360
we conducted

218
00:07:16,360 --> 00:07:18,240
a series of research.

219
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:19,760
We did a cultural research

220
00:07:19,760 --> 00:07:20,400
to find out

221
00:07:20,400 --> 00:07:22,760
what cultural factors

222
00:07:22,760 --> 00:07:25,880
are shared by parents in Western countries

223
00:07:25,880 --> 00:07:26,680
to make them

224
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:29,280
more likely to suffer from parental burnout.

225
00:07:29,280 --> 00:07:31,880
Before we start

226
00:07:31,880 --> 00:07:33,640
