291
00:09:23,120 --> 00:09:24,560
is that we don't hold

292
00:09:24,560 --> 00:09:25,840
any research assumptions.

293
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:28,400
We directly ask a research question

294
00:09:28,400 --> 00:09:29,440
and collect data.

295
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:30,720
We directly

296
00:09:30,720 --> 00:09:32,280
let our theoretical framework

297
00:09:32,280 --> 00:09:34,280
appear in our data.

298
00:09:34,280 --> 00:09:35,720
This research method

299
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:36,520
is very important.

300
00:09:36,520 --> 00:09:37,640
We have to use this method

301
00:09:37,640 --> 00:09:38,960
to explore

302
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:41,200
what kind of phenomenon

303
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:42,720
can help us understand

304
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:45,000
the cross-cultural difference

